Sentencas: Single-phase LaBaCo2O6-delta oxide, promising as oxygen storage or cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells, was prepared using two stage annealing technique.
Titulo: Preparation, oxygen nonstoichiometry and defect structure of double perovskite LaBaCo2O6-δ

Sentencas: Its oxygen nonstoichiometry (delta) was measured as a function of oxygen partial pressure (pO(2)) at temperatures (T) between 500 and 800 degrees C using thermo-gravimetric technique.
Titulo: Preparation, oxygen nonstoichiometry and defect structure of double perovskite LaBaCo2O6-δ

Sentencas: The defect structure analysis for LaBaCo2O6-delta was carried out.
Titulo: Preparation, oxygen nonstoichiometry and defect structure of double perovskite LaBaCo2O6-δ

Sentencas: The model proposed was shown to coincide well with the data on oxygen content.
Titulo: Preparation, oxygen nonstoichiometry and defect structure of double perovskite LaBaCo2O6-δ
